       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYROLL-CALC.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 EMPLOYEE-COUNT PIC 9(3) VALUE 0.
       01 HOURS-WORKED PIC 9(3)V9 VALUE 0.
       01 HOURLY-RATE PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 25.50.
       01 GROSS-PAY PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 TAX-AMOUNT PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 NET-PAY PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 TOTAL-PAYROLL PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
       01 OVERTIME-HOURS PIC 9(3)V9 VALUE 0.
       01 REGULAR-HOURS PIC 9(3)V9 VALUE 40.0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PROCESS.
           PERFORM INITIALIZE-VARS.
           PERFORM PROCESS-EMPLOYEES UNTIL EMPLOYEE-COUNT > 5.
           PERFORM DISPLAY-TOTALS.
           STOP RUN.

       INITIALIZE-VARS.
           MOVE 0 TO EMPLOYEE-COUNT.
           MOVE 0 TO TOTAL-PAYROLL.
           DISPLAY "Payroll Processing Started".

       PROCESS-EMPLOYEES.
           ADD 1 TO EMPLOYEE-COUNT.
           MOVE 45.5 TO HOURS-WORKED.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-GROSS-PAY.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-TAXES.
           PERFORM CALCULATE-NET-PAY.
           ADD NET-PAY TO TOTAL-PAYROLL.

       CALCULATE-GROSS-PAY.
           IF HOURS-WORKED > REGULAR-HOURS THEN
               SUBTRACT REGULAR-HOURS FROM HOURS-WORKED GIVING OVERTIME-HOURS
               COMPUTE GROSS-PAY = REGULAR-HOURS * HOURLY-RATE +
                                  OVERTIME-HOURS * HOURLY-RATE * 1.5
           ELSE
               COMPUTE GROSS-PAY = HOURS-WORKED * HOURLY-RATE
           END-IF.

       CALCULATE-TAXES.
           MULTIPLY GROSS-PAY BY 0.20 GIVING TAX-AMOUNT.

       CALCULATE-NET-PAY.
           SUBTRACT TAX-AMOUNT FROM GROSS-PAY GIVING NET-PAY.

       DISPLAY-TOTALS.
           DISPLAY "Total Employees Processed".
           DISPLAY EMPLOYEE-COUNT.
           DISPLAY "Total Payroll Amount".
           DISPLAY TOTAL-PAYROLL.